Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.82,0:21:26.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}这一刻 请你不要回头看我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:39.57,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}在傍晚摇曳的风中 近在咫尺的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:52.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}我一直 凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:58.86,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:05.51,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}一直喜欢着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.48,0:22:11.33,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}即使这份恋情永远也不能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:14.65,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}即使会让我受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:19.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}我也想一次又一次的让你感受到这份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:23.41,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}好想告诉你
