Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子去参加学园祭的庆祝会了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子也开始常常往外跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她爸 等爽子有了男朋友就不止是往外跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 爽子嫁人的时候就更不止这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.52,0:01:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不远了哦 她爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:45.56,logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\blur1\3c&HE7BB9A&\c&H834131&}第11话 学园祭之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子他们是不是已经到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家两个人可是约好了一起去参加庆祝会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等很久了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是刚到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.14,0:02:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种对话 肯定会出现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真想赶快围观她们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会翘掉庆功会 然后两个人一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我肯定会揍风早的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来想偷看一眼的 却没偷成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这反应算什么嘛 好受伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤？对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太紧张了 有点...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 的确是紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有点不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部 我想要你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像做梦一样 爽~子~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 那里只是牵手了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 没抱上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是牵了个手而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 骗人吧 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想围观 太给力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 那里的距离感...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:03:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 风早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人没看到现场版 所以我在给大家重现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位同学 话说昨天他们还在教室里...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以揍你一顿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 刚刚的那算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.01,0:04:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 风早喜欢贞子吗 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像做梦一样 是噩梦？还是美梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你俩是一起来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 你们两个在交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,额 额 该从哪里开始说 那个 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 为啥会这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子是怎么把风早弄到手的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我喜欢爽子喜欢到不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也惊讶啊 我真是同情风早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白...吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 这样回答就好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是急死我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能明白 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 貌似是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不是貌似了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}好强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子好强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把风早...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子的名字不是白叫的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膜拜下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我也早日成双成对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情好像朝着神奇的方向发展了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他俩看起来挺幸福的 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜了也不会有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:06:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝贺二年级D班获得学园祭第六名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要去相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以留在他的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于他来说...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可恶 哥的高级寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}讨厌啦 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 你小子不是三浦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是小痞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子带着别的班的女生在这里晃悠什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有自己班的庆功会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去 但是是这边先邀请我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了痞老师 在这种地方一个人寂寞的喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 老师寂寞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我们班的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜蜜草莓时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白成功版翔太君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧啊 看起来不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 风早 过来下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问啦 就一下下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那俩人搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他俩关系有这么好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}黑沼 黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后不要再让贞子哭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道那天贞子在学校后院哭的原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为她以为风早喜欢上了别的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有人告诉她了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁告诉她的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉她的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你做的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,败露了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 不是贞子 是爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以叫她爽子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 我还是会用我自己的爱称
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你昨天对翔太说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天...我都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘 声音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小痞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太 给哥过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你俩 在交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 该不会就你一个人这么想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有清楚直接的对黑沼说过“请和我交往”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 但是她应该明白...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了 你觉得她是能心领神会的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在赶快去说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她的样子 好像真的不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和我结婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想这么说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:09:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚蛋 快滚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得你能有今天是托了谁的福啊 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我考虑一下啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}喂 黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用追上去解释吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你都做了些什么好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么情况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 这真是最糟糕的情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子一看就不是能开玩笑的那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她当真了 你却告诉她那是个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会很伤心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会伤心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是那啥 别说交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好 你小子就等着被甩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就自己去折腾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 爸爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我会早点回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 如果我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我嫁人了 爸爸会是什么心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还是不说了 忘记我刚刚说的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 她爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是小痞说的那样 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结 结婚的事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早 你是想说结婚的事情是误会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 想打我的话就打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 再怎么说我也不会把那种话当真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道 那是荒井老师说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:13:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(643,49)\fs26}请让我考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(191,47)}请让我妄想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞 哪里有个洞让我钻进去...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想要想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么美好的事情 也只能在想像中看到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 似乎是我变得太贪心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你真的是不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么重要的事情 一定要清楚的告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则 就会永远止步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:14:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会永远好好珍惜你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远 永远...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有件重要的事情没有告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了不要讨厌我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会讨厌你的 有什么话就说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没有办法用不带私心的眼神去看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会讨厌你啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 根本用不着担心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 让人羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 说实话了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 只是觉得他俩太般配了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 真是不该说他是离爽子最远的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对谁说的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对谁说的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对风早...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早和爽子闹别扭之前...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放过她吧 结果好就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是 去找其他班的女生去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 千草啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C班也有二次聚会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子呢 甜蜜草莓时间中？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如您所料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一手嘛 贞子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(这不是梦)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(NOT梦 去看日记吧)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(看啊)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\frz17.883\pos(374,72)\c&H62695D&\3c&HD7DBCF&}注意 特别强调 这篇日记不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\frz17.883\c&H62695D&\3c&HD7DBCF&\pos(321,252)}他穿着很合适
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\frz17.883\c&H62695D&\3c&HD7DBCF&\pos(545,247)}这是我缝的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\frz17.883\c&H62695D&\3c&HD7DBCF&\pos(684,137)}庆功会的时候 他穿的是便装
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡醒之后 怎么想都觉得这是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡觉之前自己做的这一堆准备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是真的啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似大家都在讨论什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用黑魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子把风早？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说告白的时候风早的眼睛是红色的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢 喜欢 欢喜 欢...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恐怖 那不是完全被操纵了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说我就能接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别抢 按顺序来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里排队做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:18:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受过被魔法咨询的人可是全部都告白成功了诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受人敬畏吧 被人膜拜吧 爽子已经成神了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收费吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像骗子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 要真有那么好的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子不早就找到一个超好的男人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 周围净是些和尚头 废柴和笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没有遭人骚扰真是万幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看来没什么可担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式神有不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 风早...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也相信我有魔力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 现在还在想这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐都懒得吐槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了 不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是我一直都喜欢她而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说是真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候眼睛真的红了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说曹操...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早说了 他只是一直都喜欢爽子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说了 就像做梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们知道什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的班的人也都聚在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就把话说清楚 让他们都闭嘴不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他们爽子是你的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 好生动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接用了一个现实感十足的词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在真的满心都是倾心已久得偿所愿的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就不要烦我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 整理一下就是这样的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\3c&H687A73&\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(160,7)}就像做梦一样（上）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\pos(676,9)}{\3c&H687A73&\c&HFFFFFF&}如愿以偿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(606,231)}{\3c&H687A73&\c&HFFFFFF&}倾心已久\N想要你的全部\N甜蜜草莓时间(中)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(462,340)}{\3c&H687A73&\c&HFFFFFF&}男朋友     重度痴迷      女朋友（下）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(242,213)\frz20.53}{\3c&H687A73&\c&HFFFFFF&}非\N常\N非\N常\N喜\N欢\N（左）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES 就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就请大家帮忙广为宣传吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说不要烦我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子已经是恩爱十足了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 庆功会的时候也是 尤其是风早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事到如今真是怀疑 为什么当初就没有发现他们这么般配
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 很自然嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:20:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没想到胡桃会失恋 贞子会得胜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不会想到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
